entries.journal_entry_description: Cora wants you to find out what happened to Captain Donovan, the pilot of the crashed ship.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Cora wants you to return to the Deflarian camp where the medical supplies were recovered and search for more clues as to what happened to Donovan.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: It appears from a scan of the area they are using a courier for deliveries between the camps. Find and follow the courier to see where he goes.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Cora wants you to locate and track a courier she suspects is moving between the camps.  You may have to wait until the courier returns from whatever he was doing.
entries.task04_task_display_string_2: Find out where the courier is going to
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Kill the courier and find out what it is he is carrying
entries.task06_comm_message_text: It appears from an entry in the log that Donovan is in the bunker. Find and talk to him.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: The courier's log book mentioned that Donovan is in the bunker. Locate him and speak with him.
entries.task08_comm_message_text: If Donovan is to be set free, you must clear out that place.  I don't want any harm to come to him.  Kill the underboss and 8 henchmen, then kill Vindros and retrieve the key to Donovan's shackles.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: If Donovan is to escape the way must be cleared.  Defeat the underboss and 8 Henchmen.  Defeat Vinros and recover the key to Donovan's Shackles.
entries.task09_task_display_string_3: Defeat Vinros and recover the key
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: Let Donovan know the way is clear to escape
entries.task11_journal_entry_description: Return to Cora and let her know Donovan is safe
entries.task12_journal_entry_description: This is one of three tasks required to free Donovan from the bunker.
entries.task12_journal_entry_title: Defeat Vinros and retrieve the key
entries.task13_journal_entry_description: This is one of three tasks required to free Donovan from the bunker.
